"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.1.2.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.1.2.1</span> 標題：鎖（lock）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： כַּף, מַנְעוּל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kaf man‘ul)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:5\">SNG 5:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： נעל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： na‘al)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:23\">JDG 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:24\">JDG 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:17\">2SA 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:18\">2SA 13:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： סגר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： sagar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:51\">JDG 9:51</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κλεῖθρον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kleithron)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:17\">LJE 1:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κλείω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kleiō)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:10\">MAT 25:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:7\">LUK 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:19\">JHN 20:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:26\">JHN 20:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:23\">ACT 5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:30\">ACT 21:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir42:6\">SIR 42:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:14\">BEL 1:14</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\" data-image-id=\"WEB-0403_lock_hant\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" alt=\"WEB-0403_lock_hant\"></figure>鎖是一種用來固定門的裝置，只有使用一把特殊的鑰匙才能將鎖打開（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.2 鑰匙 (key)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.2&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:5\">SNG 5:5</a> 中，希伯來文短語<em>kaf man‘ul</em> 可能是指一個木製突起物或一根繩子，用來拉開門閂，使門打開。可以譯為「門的把手」（“handle of the door”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ），或「門閂的把手」（“handles of the bolt”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Standard Bible\">NASB</abbr> ），或「鎖的把手」（“handles of the lock”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"King James Version (1611)\">KJV</abbr> ），也可以簡單地譯為「門」（“door”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0081_door_locked_with_bar.png\" alt=\"門和門閂\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">門和門閂 (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:18\">LJE 1:18</a> 使用了這個不常見的希臘文，可以指鎖（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ），也可以指橫著擋住門的閂（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
